Interface LdapTO.JSONFIELDS

  • Enclosing class:
    LdapTO

    public static interface LdapTO.JSONFIELDS
    The fields of this transfer object, that is their names in the JSON world. For example, in the user interface world a field would be named "ldap.serverURL". The base name builds the first part, the second part is the specific field.
